{
  "name": "Font",
  "summary": "<p>如果不想将单元格中的文本或图形设为相同的格式，则使用 <strong>Characters</strong> 属性返回文本的子集。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong>Font</strong> 属性可返回 <strong>Font</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将工作表 Sheet1中单元格 A1:C5 区域中的字体设为加粗*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:C5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Bold</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示第一个工作表中D1单元格的字体样式*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> font = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`字体样式为 <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${font.FontStyle}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>包含对象的字体属性（字体名称、字号、颜色等等）。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a>**对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n}\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Background",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th>XlBackground 可为以下常量之一。</th>\n<th>文本背景描述</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>xlBackgroundAutomatic</strong></td>\n<td>字体背景将自动更改文本周围的背景区域颜色，以使在文本下方元素所应用的颜色之上显示的文本达到最佳效果</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlBackgroundOpaque</strong></td>\n<td>如果文本颜色与文本下的填充颜色非常接近或者为同一颜色，则字体背景会设置为空，以便不显示文本</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlBackgroundTransparent</strong></td>\n<td>字体背景设置为透明，以便当文本颜色接近文本下方的颜色时，文本背景不会更改</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置图表中使用的文本的背景类型。<strong>Variant</strong> 类型，可读写。可将其设置为 **<a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlBackground 枚举.html\">XlBackground</a>**常量之一。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例为第一张工作表上的第一张嵌入图表添加图表标题，然后设置标题的字体大小和背景类型。本示例假定图表在第一张工作表上。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chart = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>\n    chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasTitle</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartTitle</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Rainfall Totals by Month&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> font = chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartTitle</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>\n    font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Size</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n    font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Background</span> = xlBackgroundTransparent\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将 A2 单元格的背景类型设置为 xlBackgroundOpaque 。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Background</span> = xlBackgroundOpaque\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Bold",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果字体格式为加粗，则该属性值为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Variant</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将工作表 Sheet1中单元格 A1:A5 区域中的字体设为加粗*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Bold</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一个工作表中的单元格A1字体是否为加粗。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> bold = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Bold</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(bold)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Color",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th>对象</th>\n<th>对应颜色</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>Border</strong></td>\n<td>边框的颜色。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Borders</strong></td>\n<td>一个区域的所有四条边的颜色。如果四边不是同一种颜色，则 <strong>Color</strong> 返回的是 0（零）。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Font</strong></td>\n<td>字体的颜色。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Interior</strong></td>\n<td>单元格底纹的颜色或图形对象的填充颜色。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Tab</strong></td>\n<td>选项卡的颜色。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置对象的主要颜色，如注释部分中的表格所示。使用 <strong>RGB</strong> 函数可创建颜色值。<strong>Variant</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例对 Chart1 ���数值坐标轴的刻度线标志颜色进行设置*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Axes</span>(xlValue).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TickLabels</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将工作表Sheet1的单元格 A1:A4 区域中的字体颜色设置为蓝色*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> font = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>\n    font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ColorIndex",
      "summary": "<p>颜色可指定为当前调色板中颜色的索引值，也可指定为下列 <strong>XlColorIndex</strong> 常量之一：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>xlColorIndexAutomatic</strong></li>\n<li><strong>xlColorIndexNone</strong></li>\n</ul>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Variant</strong> 值，它代表字体的颜色。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将 Sheet1 上 A1 单元格的字体颜色更改为红色*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例判断D3单元格的字体颜色是否为自动配色，不是则设置字体颜色为绿色*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> font = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> == xlColorIndexAutomatic) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`字体颜色为自动配色`</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "FontStyle",
      "summary": "<p>更改该属性可能会影响其他 <strong>Font</strong> 属性（例如 <strong>Bold</strong> 和 <strong>Italic</strong>）。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置字体样式。<strong>String</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将 Sheet1 中 A1 单元格的字体样式设置为加粗和倾斜*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FontStyle</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Bold Italic&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示C1单元格的字体样式*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> font = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`字体样式为 <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${font.FontStyle}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Italic",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果字体样式为倾斜，则该属性值为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将 Sheet1 中 A1:A5 区域的字形设置为倾斜*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Italic</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一个工作表中单��格D2的字形是否为倾斜。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> font = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Italic</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Name",
      "summary": "<p><strong>Font</strong> 对象的名称为 <strong>String</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Variant</strong> 值，它代表对象的名称。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一个工作表中单元格 B2:C3 区域的字体名称设置为黑体。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> font = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B2:C3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>\n    font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断第一个工作表中单元格E3的字体名称是否为宋体，是则将字形设置为倾斜，不是则设置字体名称为黑体*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> font = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;宋体&quot;</span>) {\n        font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Italic</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`字体名称为宋体，已将字形设置为倾斜`</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`字体名称已设置为黑体`</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Size",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置字号。可读/写 <strong>Variant</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
