    {
      "name": "Strikethrough",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果文字中间有一条水平删除线，则该属性值为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将 Sheet1 中活动单元格的字体设置为加删除线*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveCell</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Strikethrough</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断第一个工作表中单元格D5的字体如果有删除线，则通知用户，并取消删除线*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> font = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Strikethrough</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;取消字体的删除线&quot;</span>)\n        font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Strikethrough</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
