      "description": "<p>如果字体格式设置为下标，则该属性值为 <strong>True</strong>。默认值为 <strong>False</strong>。<strong>Variant</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将工作表Sheet1中 A1 单元格的第二个字符设置为下标字符*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Subscript</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一个工作表中单元格D1的字体格式是否设置为下标字体*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> font = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Subscript</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Superscript",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果字体格式设置为上标字符，则该属性值为 <strong>True</strong>；默认值为 <strong>False</strong>。<strong>Variant</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将工作表Sheet1中 A1 单元格的最后一个字符设置为上标字符*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> n = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>(n, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Superscript</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断第一个工作表中单元格B3的字体格式是否为上标字符，如果不是则将字体格式设置为上标字符。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> font = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Superscript</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;字体格式为上标字符&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Superscript</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;字体格式已设置为上标字符&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ThemeColor",
      "summary": "<p>如果对象当前未应用主题颜色，试图访问其主题颜色则会引起无效请求运行时错误。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置已应用的配色方案中的主题颜色，该配色方案与指定对象相关联。可读/写 <strong>Variant</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一个工作表中单元格 A1:D3 区域的字体主题颜色设置为强调文字颜色6*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:D3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = msoThemeColorAccent6\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一个工作表中单元格B5的字体主题颜色是否为强调文字色1*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> font = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> == xlThemeColorAccent1)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ThemeFont",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置与指定对象关联的应用字体方案中的主题字体。可读/写 **<a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlThemeFont 枚举.html\">XlThemeFont</a>**类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将Sheet1中活动单元格的字体的主题字体设置为主题正文*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveCell</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeFont</span> = xlThemeFontMinor\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断工作表Sheet1中单元格A5的字体的主题字体是否为主题标题，不是则设置其字体大小为16磅*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> font = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeFont</span> == xlThemeFontMajor) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;字体的主题字体是主题标题&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        font.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Size</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">16</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
